01:26.319 --> 01:27.654
Okay, whose idea was it

01:27.688 --> 01:29.489
to go to the zoo
in the middle of winter?

01:33.894 --> 01:35.829
What a great day for the zoo.

01:37.798 --> 01:39.700
Balki, take off
the elephant nose.

01:41.602 --> 01:43.570
It was embarrassing enough
at the restaurant.

01:45.539 --> 01:47.608
Oh, come on, cousin.
Lighten up.

01:47.641 --> 01:49.676
Why you don’t put on
your alligator nose?

01:51.377 --> 01:53.847
The nose goes on, I go out.

01:57.718 --> 01:59.185
[knocking on door]

02:02.222 --> 02:03.824
Balk‐eye Bartookamouse?

02:08.328 --> 02:09.930
I’m Balk‐eye.

02:09.963 --> 02:12.132
Could you please sign your name?

02:20.206 --> 02:21.608
With a pen.

02:33.319 --> 02:34.788
There you go.

02:35.556 --> 02:36.823
Thank you.

02:37.924 --> 02:40.293
What is it, Balki?

02:40.326 --> 02:42.362
It’s from Mypos.

02:42.395 --> 02:43.764
No kidding.

02:45.732 --> 02:47.200
[Balki gasping]

02:52.706 --> 02:54.240
Oh, what, did
the village idiot die

02:54.274 --> 02:55.742
and they sent you his hat?

03:00.013 --> 03:02.716
Cousin, show some respect.

03:04.951 --> 03:06.452
This is the headpiece worn

03:06.486 --> 03:08.955
by the official negotiator
on Mypos.

03:08.989 --> 03:11.925
No negotiating can take
place without this hat.

03:11.958 --> 03:14.895
We call it The Hat
Of A Thousand Quibbles.

03:16.963 --> 03:17.998
Well, it’s beautiful.

03:18.031 --> 03:20.200
Does it come with instructions?

03:21.568 --> 03:23.504
Well, there’s a letter.

03:28.041 --> 03:30.210
It’s from King Ferdinand.

03:32.946 --> 03:33.814
Must be important.

03:33.847 --> 03:36.517
He wrote it on his
Garfield stationery.

03:40.053 --> 03:41.655
"Dear Balki.

03:41.688 --> 03:45.826
"A company in Chicago
called Worldwide Amalgamated

03:45.859 --> 03:49.029
"wants to buy
500 acres of land

03:49.062 --> 03:51.297
"on the north shore of Mypos.

03:52.866 --> 03:55.902
"And we want..."

03:55.936 --> 03:58.672
He wants me
to negotiate the sale.

03:58.705 --> 04:01.374
And they, they set up
a meeting for tomorrow.

04:01.407 --> 04:04.277
Excuse me. I’ve got
to start my preparations.

