get out of your way.

04:53.493 --> 04:54.761
Bye, Balki.

04:54.795 --> 04:56.563
Bye, Mary Anne.

04:57.864 --> 04:59.065
Goodnight.

04:59.099 --> 05:00.934
Bye, Larry.

05:00.967 --> 05:02.836
Goodnight.

05:02.869 --> 05:04.805
‐Bye.
‐Bye‐bye now.

05:07.608 --> 05:08.809
