05:12.513 --> 05:13.847
‐Balki.
‐Yes.

05:13.880 --> 05:15.816
What are you doing?

05:17.483 --> 05:18.752
I’m doing the Hongi Bongi.

05:21.788 --> 05:24.891
It’s the, the ritual
of purification.

05:24.925 --> 05:27.661
I must be worthy
to wear the hat.

05:27.694 --> 05:30.764
Also, it makes my negotiating
hormones kick in.

