Please be seated.

10:49.950 --> 10:52.385
Gentlemen, I trust
you’re familiar

10:52.418 --> 10:54.921
with the piece
of land in question?

10:54.955 --> 10:56.389
Familiar with it?

10:56.422 --> 10:57.758
I, when I was a boy we used
to go there every Saturday‐‐

10:57.791 --> 11:00.026
Balki! Yes, uh, yes.

11:00.060 --> 11:01.862
Yes, we are, Mr. Stanhouse

11:01.895 --> 11:03.764
and I must compliment you

11:03.797 --> 11:06.299
on your astute knowledge
of valuable real estate.

11:08.835 --> 11:10.270
‐Mr. Outhouse.
‐Oh.

11:14.808 --> 11:16.242
A question.

11:16.276 --> 11:21.081
Why does your company
want 500 acres on Mypos?

11:21.114 --> 11:24.250
Audits indicate that our debt
ratio is highly underleveraged

11:24.284 --> 11:26.787
and in order to avoid
certain tax liabilities

11:26.820 --> 11:29.723
we need to invest capital before
the end of our fiscal year.

11:29.756 --> 11:32.358
Ha ha ha, I know
the problem well.

11:34.094 --> 11:35.796
Now, we’re prepared to pay
a very fair price

11:35.829 --> 11:36.997
for the land in question.

11:37.030 --> 11:38.264
In addition, the two of you

11:38.298 --> 11:40.333
will be receiving
a negotiator’s fee

11:40.366 --> 11:43.069
of ten percent
of the total purchase price.

11:45.238 --> 11:47.407
Now, after careful examination

11:47.440 --> 11:49.375
of the land on that part
of the island‐‐

11:49.409 --> 11:51.978
We get money?

11:52.012 --> 11:55.181
Ten percent, to be paid
by Worldwide of course.

11:55.215 --> 11:57.150
‐Now‐‐
‐We get money?

11:59.019 --> 12:03.824
Gentlemen, for
the 500 acres indicated

12:03.857 --> 12:05.325
Worldwide Amalgamated

12:05.358 --> 12:09.362
will pay to the island
of Mypos $28 million.

12:09.395 --> 12:12.232
Sold! Sold!
It’s a deal!

12:28.982 --> 12:31.184
Sold! It’s a deal!
Here, where‐where do we sign?

12:31.217 --> 12:33.219
Here, here, use my pen.
You can use my pen.

12:33.253 --> 12:35.221
Here we go! Here we go!

12:39.492 --> 12:41.327
Cousin Larry can’t say "sold."

12:41.361 --> 12:44.297
Only the head negotiator
can say "sold."

12:44.330 --> 12:46.366
Of course.
I got a little excited.

12:46.399 --> 12:48.902
Go ahead, Balki,
you’re the head negotiator.

12:48.935 --> 12:50.403
Say "sold!"

12:58.311 --> 13:00.581
As the head negotiator

13:00.614 --> 13:03.917
I’m going to have to study it

13:03.950 --> 13:07.320
consider it, meditate on it.

13:07.353 --> 13:08.922
I’ll get back to you

13:08.955 --> 13:13.059
say the second Tuesday
after the new moon?

13:13.093 --> 13:14.861
I must inform you, sir

13:14.895 --> 13:16.062
that Worldwide Amalgamated

13:16.096 --> 13:18.164
is interested
in other properties

13:18.198 --> 13:21.001
so our offer is only good
till 10 a. m. tomorrow.

13:26.172 --> 13:30.944
(Larry)
’Balki, we are being offered
ten percent of $28 million’

13:30.977 --> 13:33.847
if you just say "yes."

13:33.880 --> 13:36.550
Cousin, people don’t pay
millions of dollars

13:36.583 --> 13:38.151
for something
that’s worthless.

13:38.184 --> 13:39.419
Of course they do!

13:39.452 --> 13:42.022
George Steinbrenner
does it all the time.

13:45.391 --> 13:46.292
I don’t know, cousin.

13:46.326 --> 13:48.494
I‐I still have a funny
feeling about it.

13:48.529 --> 13:51.097
Balki, what more
do you need to know?

13:51.131 --> 13:52.365
Worldwide Amalgamated is one

13:52.398 --> 13:54.400
of the nicest
multinational corporations

13:54.434 --> 13:56.436
in the Fortune 500.

13:56.469 --> 13:58.371
Yeah, we read the annual reports

13:58.404 --> 14:01.608
the press releases, the cover
story in Time magazine.

14:01.642 --> 14:03.610
I got this microfilm.

14:03.644 --> 14:05.078
But reading the tiny print

14:05.111 --> 14:06.913
is giving me a headache.

14:08.414 --> 14:10.617
Alright.
Balki, let’s focus here.

14:11.484 --> 14:15.155
Now, could $28 million

14:15.188 --> 14:19.025
improve the lives
of the people on Mypos?

14:19.059 --> 14:20.326
‐Yes.
‐Yes?

14:20.360 --> 14:23.463
Yes. We could,
we could build better roads.

14:23.496 --> 14:24.998
Better roads.

14:25.031 --> 14:27.267
‐New schools.
‐New schools!

14:27.300 --> 14:30.070
And there has been talk of,
of building a football stadium

14:30.103 --> 14:32.038
and luring the Raiders over.

14:33.640 --> 14:36.376
Well, Balki.
This is your chance.

14:36.409 --> 14:37.611
Mypos will have the Raiders!

14:37.644 --> 14:40.514
The Raiderettes!
The silver and black!

14:40.547 --> 14:43.383
You mean,
Bo knows sheepherding?

14:46.119 --> 14:47.654
Yes.

14:47.688 --> 14:49.089
Yes, he does.

14:50.190 --> 14:53.694
So, in the morning
you’ll accept this offer

14:53.727 --> 14:55.896
and we’ll get
expensive haircuts.

14:57.397 --> 14:59.499
Oh, cousin,
I wish I could say yes!

14:59.533 --> 15:01.134
‐You can.
‐I can?

15:01.167 --> 15:02.468
Yes, you can.

15:04.304 --> 15:07.107
‐No, I can’t.
‐Why not?

15:07.140 --> 15:09.442
Because I don’t know why
Worldwide wants to buy the land.

15:09.475 --> 15:11.512
Balki, they told you why
they want to buy the land.

15:11.545 --> 15:13.046
They’ve got a tax problem.

15:13.079 --> 15:14.715
In fact, if you’d say yes

15:14.748 --> 15:16.449
we would have one problem.

15:16.482 --> 15:18.685
A big, beautiful,
kiss it on the mouth

15:18.719 --> 15:21.688
$2.8 million tax problem.

15:23.256 --> 15:25.325
[knocking on door]

15:25.358 --> 15:29.295
Cousin, I want you
to calm down.

15:29.329 --> 15:31.364
You’re getting
a greed‐high again.

15:32.999 --> 15:34.234
[knocking on door]

15:36.169 --> 15:38.104
Why is this so hard?

15:40.006 --> 15:41.642
Balk‐eye Bartookamouse?

15:44.110 --> 15:45.512
I’m Balk‐eye.

15:45.546 --> 15:47.447
Could you please sign...

15:47.480 --> 15:50.183
Uh, take this pen
and sign your name.

16:10.036 --> 16:12.372
It’s from Worldwide.

16:12.405 --> 16:16.276
"Dear, Mr. Bartokomous,
effective immediately

16:16.309 --> 16:22.315
"Worldwide Amalgamated withdraws
its offer of $28 million.

16:22.348 --> 16:25.686
"Further evaluation
of the land in question

16:25.719 --> 16:28.121
makes it prudent..."

16:28.154 --> 16:31.692
Balki. I’m going
to the window now.

16:33.760 --> 16:36.563
If you need me,
I’ll be on the pavement.

16:38.164 --> 16:39.766
Take a sweater.

16:42.302 --> 16:44.571
(Balki)
’"So effective immediately’

16:44.605 --> 16:49.175
we are raising our offer
to $35 million."

16:51.645 --> 16:55.281
$35 million?

16:55.315 --> 16:58.051
Balki, you are a genius.

17:02.488 --> 17:04.625
You held out and squeezed

17:04.657 --> 17:07.127
another $7 million
out of them.

17:07.160 --> 17:09.194
Do you think it would be
too much if we hired a butler?

17:11.832 --> 17:14.200
It seems like this is an offer
I can’t refuse.

17:14.233 --> 17:17.403
You can’t refuse? You can’t
refuse? He can’t refuse!

17:17.436 --> 17:19.039
What are you going to do
with your share of the money?

17:20.272 --> 17:21.473
I give it to the poor.

17:21.508 --> 17:22.643
Good. They’ll be taken care of.

17:22.675 --> 17:24.778
I can spend my share on myself.

17:41.795 --> 17:44.264
Mr. Bartokomous
is 20 minutes late.

17:44.297 --> 17:46.332
If he doesn’t get here soon
to sign those papers

17:46.366 --> 17:47.701
I’m afraid our deal is off.

17:47.734 --> 17:49.169
Oh, don’t worry.
He’ll be here any minute.

17:49.202 --> 17:51.171
He’s very hot for this deal.

17:52.472 --> 17:54.440
What do you think
of the new Mercedes?

17:56.442 --> 17:59.546
Balki, where have you been?

17:59.580 --> 18:01.748
Mr. Bartokomous,
we were getting worried.

18:01.782 --> 18:03.183
(Balki)
I’m sorry.

18:03.216 --> 18:04.585
I‐I had to return the documents

18:04.618 --> 18:06.252
to the archive
so I wouldn’t be slapped

18:06.286 --> 18:09.122
with that ten cents
a day late charge.

18:09.155 --> 18:11.357
Mr. Bartokomous, shall
we get started?

18:11.391 --> 18:12.593
Certainly.

18:12.626 --> 18:14.394
Mr. Appleton has the contracts.

18:14.427 --> 18:15.896
All we need is your signature.

18:15.929 --> 18:17.898
Well, uh, before that

18:17.931 --> 18:20.901
there’s something
that I must do.

18:20.934 --> 18:24.505
Right, alright, alright. This,
this will just take a minute.

18:24.538 --> 18:27.140
